! Minimal Arista EOS startup-config for the inter-cluster router.
!
! Rendered by boxman via Jinja2 before `containerlab deploy`. The
! env() / env_required() helpers from boxman's jinja environment are
! available here.
!
hostname {{ env("BOXMAN_CEOS_HOSTNAME", default="router-ceos") }}
!
no aaa root
!
username admin privilege 15 role network-admin secret 0 {{ env("BOXMAN_CEOS_ADMIN_PASS", default="admin") }}
!
ip routing
!
! Ethernet1 connects to the cluster_1 transit bridge (bx_inter_a).
! Ethernet2 connects to the cluster_2 transit bridge (bx_inter_b).
!
interface Ethernet1
   description to-cluster-1-via-bx_inter_a
   no switchport
   ip address 10.10.1.1/24
!
interface Ethernet2
   description to-cluster-2-via-bx_inter_b
   no switchport
   ip address 10.10.2.1/24
!
! Both transit subnets are directly connected; the FIB has the routes
! automatically. Add `router bgp` / `router ospf` blocks here to extend.
!
management api http-commands
   no shutdown
!
end
